[[span class="disappearance2"]]**[[span class="skew change-text305"]][[span]]附件[[/span]][[span]]什么[[/span]][[span]][？][[/span]][[/span]]：**以下的音频资料是进行孔洞内部的探索尝试时记录的。[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]该次调查与之前进行的一样，通过在调查员身上系上彼此连接的特殊绳索，将其从上方的大水族箱中渐渐降下的方式进行。[[/span]]

[[div style="display: inline-block; border:dashed 1px #999999; background:#F5F5F5; float:center; width:84%; padding:1px 15px; margin: 10px 10px 10px 20px"]]

[[include :snippets:html5player
|type=audio
|url=你曾听过这声音，但你未曾仔细记住
]]

[[span class="disappearance4"]]・・・[[/span]]
 _

[[span class="disappearance3"]]**莉兹[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]研究员：**[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]调查员，请回答我。你在洞中[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]看见了什么？[[/span]]

[[span class="disappearance4"]]**D-[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]812636[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]：**[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]不行啊，老师。即使我用灯照亮四周[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]也什么都看不见。我[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]感觉这个地方[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]很令人讨厌。[[/span]]

[[span class="disappearance5"]]**埃文斯博士：**可怜的基金会员工，你愿意加入我们吗？[[/span]]

[[span class="disappearance3"]]**莉兹[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]研究员：**[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]调查员，[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]那种感觉[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]是怎样的[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]你能说清楚吗？[[/span]]

[[span class="disappearance4"]]**D-[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]812636[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]：**[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]我无法解释清楚，但我[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]感到很不安。[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]不知为什么，现在我忽然觉得[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]不知道[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]我在哪里，好可怕。[[/span]][[span class="disappearance4"]]就好像独自一人[[/span]][[span class="disappearance3"]]漂浮在周围什么都没有的大海里一样。[[/span]]

[[span class="disappearance5"]]**埃文斯博士：**如果你能听到我们的声音，恳求我们让你回到上面也可以。[[/span]]

